{"title_page": "Thindal, Erode", "text_new": "{{moresources|date=August 2018}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=August 2018}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Thindal\n| native_name             = \n| native_name_lang        = ta\n| other_name              = \n| nickname                = \n| settlement_type         = Neighborhood\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| pushpin_map             = India Tamil Nadu#India\n| pushpin_label_position  = right\n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in Tamil Nadu, India\n| coordinates             = {{coord|11.317976|N|77.676473|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|India}}\n| subdivision_type1       = [[States and territories of India|State]]\n| subdivision_name1       = [[Tamil Nadu]]\n| subdivision_type2       = [[List of districts of India|District]]\n| subdivision_name2       = Erode\n| established_title       = <!-- Established -->\n| established_date        = \n| founder                 = \n| named_for               = \n| government_type         = \n| governing_body          = \n| unit_pref               = Metric\n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_rank               = \n| area_total_km2          = \n| elevation_footnotes     = \n| elevation_m             = \n| population_total        = \n| population_as_of        = \n| population_rank         = \n| population_density_km2  = auto\n| population_demonym      = \n| population_footnotes    = \n| demographics_type1      = Languages\n| demographics1_title1    = Official\n| demographics1_info1     = [[Tamil language|Tamil]]\n| timezone1               = [[Indian Standard Time|IST]]\n| utc_offset1             = +5:30\n| postal_code_type        = [[Postal Index Number|PIN]]\n| postal_code             = 638012\n| area_code_type          = Telephone code\n| area_code               = 0424\n| registration_plate      = '''TN-56'''\n| blank1_name_sec1        = Nearest city\n| blank1_info_sec1        = Erode\n| blank2_name_sec1        = [[Lok Sabha]] constituency\n| blank2_info_sec1        = Erode\n| blank3_name_sec1        = [[Vidhan Sabha]] constituency\n| blank3_info_sec1        = Erode West\n| blank1_name_sec2        = [[Climate of India|Climate]]\n| blank1_info_sec2        = [[Climatic regions of India|Moderate]] <small>([[K\u00f6ppen climate classification|K\u00f6ppen]])</small>\n| website                 = \n| footnotes               = \n}}\n\n'''Thindal''' is a neighborhood of [[Erode]] city in [[Tamil Nadu]]. It is located 8&nbsp;km from [[Erode Junction]] and 7&nbsp;km from [[Central Bus Terminus, Erode]]. It is now officially a part of [[Erode Municipal Corporation]]. The locality is well known for the [[Thindal Murugan Temple]] (Velayudaswami temple).\n\nThis neighborhood is located along the arterial [[Perundurai Road, Erode|Perundurai Road]] which connects the city with western districts like [[Tiruppur]], [[Coimbatore]] and [[Kerala]]. [[Erode Ring Road|Outer Ring Road]] connecting all the arterial roads of the city is intersecting [[Perundurai Road, Erode|Perundurai road]] here.It is a developing area due to the initiation of various educational institutions. \n\n==Institutions in and around Thindal==\n\n*[[Vellalar College for Women]] (Government Aided-Autonomous)Since 1970  <ref>https://vcw.ac.in/</ref>\n* [https://velalarengg.ac.in/ Velalar College of Engineering and Technology] <ref>https://velalarengg.ac.in/</ref>\n*[[Vellalar College for Women|vellalar College of Education for Women]]\n* Vellalar [[Matriculation]] Higher Secondary School for Girls Since 1980\n* Vellalar High School for Girls\n* Vellalar Vidyalaya Senior Secondary School (CBSE) <ref>https://velalarcbse.com/</ref>\n* vellalar College of Nursing \n* Vellalar Teacher' Training Institute\n* Govt. High School, Thindal\n* BVB Matric Higher Secondary School, Thindal. <ref>http://thebvb.com/</ref>\n* The BVB(CBSE), Therkku pallam, Thindal.<ref> http://thebvb.com/</ref>\n* URC [[Matriculation]] School <ref>http://www.urcschool.com/</ref>\n* AET Matriculation School\n* The Indian Public School,([[Central Board of Secondary Education|CBSE]]) <ref>https://www.theindianpublicschool.org/</ref>\n* Geethanjanli All India Senior Secondary school - [[Central Board of Secondary Education|CBSE]] <ref>http://geethaanjali.edu.in/</ref>\n* CS Academy -[[Central Board of Secondary Education|CBSE]] (BVB) <ref>https://csacademy.in/</ref>\n\n==Nearby places==\n\nNearby places include [http://texvalleyindia.com/about-texvalley/ Texvalley],<ref>http://texvalleyindia.com/about-texvalley/</ref> [[Gangapuram]] (6&nbsp;km). [[Vellode Birds Sanctuary|Vellode Bird Sanctuary]] (11.5 km), [[Sangameswarar Temple|Bhavani Sangameswarar Temple]] (12.9 km), [[Villarasampatti]] (2.8&nbsp;km), Koorapalayam (5.1&nbsp;km), Ellappalayam (5.1&nbsp;km), Kavundachipalayam (5.9&nbsp;km)\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Erode district]]\n", "text_old": "{{moresources|date=August 2018}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=August 2018}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Thindal\n| native_name             = \n| native_name_lang        = ta\n| other_name              = \n| nickname                = \n| settlement_type         = Neighborhood\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| pushpin_map             = India Tamil Nadu#India\n| pushpin_label_position  = right\n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in Tamil Nadu, India\n| coordinates             = {{coord|11.317976|N|77.676473|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|India}}\n| subdivision_type1       = [[States and territories of India|State]]\n| subdivision_name1       = [[Tamil Nadu]]\n| subdivision_type2       = [[List of distr